*''[[Trypanosoma lewisi]]'', in rats
* ''[[Trypanosoma melophagium]]'' Sheep infected by ''[[Melophagus ovinus]]''
*''[[Trypanosoma percae]]'' in fish: ''[[Perca fluviatilis]]''
